				For The Aegis Of Life Quest, U have to kill 2 Lord Grimrots, 1 Live qho coned yellow to me at 34, and 1 dead skellie version who conned blue, u need the heart from the dead one and the NO DROP scythe from the live one, the will both drop another scythe but it is not the one u need for the quest. You have to give both items to Camlen In the UFO in qeynos, u have to have EXTREMLY high faction to do the Quest so make sure your getting the quest and you have maxxed out your Priest Of Life faction or u will just have waisted the items and have to do it over. You can tell when you have maxxed your PoL faction when u dont get anymore from turning in sashes. I just did the Quest, thats how u complete, i hope it helps others.
