				If anyone is wondering, the reward for this quest is the Aegis of Life, which can be worn as a shield or in the back slot.  It's stats are 12 AC, +10 Wis, +25 SV Disease, can't remember the weight, and I think it has the Effect of Superior Healing, not sure though, and it is wearable by Clerics and Paladins of any race able to be these classes.  I hear you need really high faction to do the quest, and even more INSANELY high faction to finish it and get the reward.  Lord Grimrot apparently spawns in 2 forms, an undead form of lvl 25? or so, and a live human SK form lvl 35? or so, which drops teh items you need for the quest at the undead ruins in South Karana near the bridge to North Karana.  You apparently need the Pestilence Scythe and Heart and the faction you need is with the Temple of Life.  Just my info. )
