<BR>
The quest is from the Temple of Life in Qeynos from Camlen. You must return the decaying heart of Lord Grimrot (undead form) and his no drop, lore Pestilence Scythe (from live human version). Lord Grimrot spawns in South Karana at the ruins just south of the bridge to North Karana. The faction needed for the quest is insane but doable. Basically you must have very warm faction to obtain the quest and maximum Priest of Life faction to obtain the item. You will know it is maximum when you no longer get any PoL faction from bandit sashes and PoL only from Lashun for bones and gold. Good luck all.<BR>
 
