			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Lord Grim will also spawn in skeletal form.  We got the heart from him in this form.  Your faction must be insanely high to complete the quest (and get the reward) - higher than it takes to get the quest.  If you give him (Camlend) the quest scythe and he says &quot;aren't you forgetting something...&quot; then your faction is good enough to give the heart (which is more rare tahn the scythe.)  So, use the scythe to &quot;test&quot; your faction.  Much easier to get another scythe than to get a 2nd heart. <BR>
<BR>
Good luck!<BR>
<BR>
p.s. my cleric friend is still rasing faction but he has the heart.<BR>

